Agile Organisations extend the values of the {{Agile Manifesto}} to all business functions. They take the form of a [[Holarchy]] of [[Autonomous Squad]]s facilitated by [[servant leader|Leadership as a Service]]s, not commanded by [[managers]]. Their squads [[continuously adapt|Continuous Adaptation]] their composition to fit their competencies to the creation and support of the [[features]] of their [[products and services]], and to fit these to their markets. They boldly seek out new markets through [[Agile R&D]],